{1: 'Conservation Area 221', 2: 'Babylonia Logistics Warehouse', 4: '12:30', 5: 'Line Spacing: 0'}
{3: 'As you leave the landing pad, the noisy engines behind you briefly stop before starting again.'}
{3: 'You and Ayla wave goodbye to the pilot through the windshield, then turn toward your destination.'}
{3: 'You press the terminal amidst the roaring air currents. The rumbling drowns out the sound in your earpiece.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: "The storage area in front of you is the smallest range you've been able to narrow down. The frame was transferred to the conservation area a week ago.", 4: '18'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Item transfers within the storage area aren't reported to Babylonia, and from the current situation, I doubt they're even recorded locally.", 4: '18'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: "Got it. So it's time to search, right?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'I can show you which warehouses have the good stuff. This conservation area has loads of art on the restricted list.', 4: '18'}
{2: "Now there'll be two more names on the list.", 3: '22'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Don't worry, I can take off my name and Ayla's, and put yours.", 4: '18'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiStoryBlackPassScene.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory759.jpg'}
{3: 'You arrive at the entrance, chatting along the way.'}
{3: 'Uneasiness rises as you walk up to the doorway.'}
{2: 'Teddy, check our surroundings.', 3: '33'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiTheatre3/FxUiTheatre3PlayMainScreenBlueEx.prefab', 2: '2'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiTheatre3/FxUiTheatre3PlayMainScreenBlueEx.prefab'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: 'All 47 cameras around you are functional. No signs of tampering were detected.', 4: '18'}
{3: 'Ayla senses the change in atmosphere and tilts her head.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Ayla', 3: 'Commandant? Did you notice something?', 4: '1'}
{2: "It's going a bit too smoothly.", 3: '50'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Smooth? Not really. According to puzzle game logic, we need multiple keys to unlock the path we're taking.", 4: '18'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "We've just started. The Construct in this warehouse might only be the start, and we still have no idea what's going on with Ishmael.", 4: '18'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: '...I think what the commandant means is that everything seems to be going in a straight line.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'You nod to Ayla and instinctively move your hand toward your holster.'}
{2: 'Identify problem, gather clues, locate target.', 3: '57'}
{2: 'This is almost too easy.', 3: '58'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Yes, and we didn't even need to solve the only trouble we ran into.", 4: '18'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Thinking about it now, our initial search showed no results until an error message suddenly gave us a clue. It's odd, no matter how you look at it.", 4: '18'}
{3: 'Realizing the problem, the voice in your earpiece grows more alert.'}
{2: "If this isn't just coincidence or the task is actually straightforward...", 3: '63'}
{2: 'Ayla', 3: "Then we've stumbled into someone else's game.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'You exchange a look with Ayla, silently becoming alert as you enter the warehouse side by side.'}
